Patches applied:

 * joachim.falk@gmx.de--2004-jf-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.1--patch-22
   
 * Merge from joachim.falk@gmx.de--2005-common-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.1 and
              joachim.falk@gmx.de--2006-common-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.2
 - No longer use INCLUDES to specify cpp include use AM_CPPFLAGS instead
   as INCLUDES has been declared obsolete by automake
 - Added %:%.m4 rule to jfrules.mk
   Modified %.sh: %-sh, %: %.m4, %.c: %.re2c, and %.cpp: %.re2cpp
   to generate the target directory if necessary
 - Eliminated NL generation in m4/jfsuggar.m4
 - do not force libtool searching includes in ".libs"
 - Improve support for doxygen-doc target
   enable support for recursion
   Fixed doxygen support for cases where both jfrules.mk and doxygen.am
   are included via automake
 - Added copyright to doxygen.am
 - Split up all.m4 into smaller chunks moved obsolete stuff to dustbin

 * joachim.falk@gmx.de--2004-jf-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.1--patch-23
   
 * Merge from BuildSystem--mainline--0.2 branch
 - Added COPYRIGHT and LICENSE files
 - Added copyright boilerplate to all source files
 - Readded copyright of Oren Ben-Kiki for doxygen.am

 * joachim.falk@gmx.de--2004-jf-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.1--patch-24
   
 * Merge from joachim.falk@gmx.de--2006-common-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.2 branch
 - Uncoditionally define pkg_<pkgname>_srcdir and pkg_<pkgname>_builddir
   even if action if found is given
 - Define shell variable acjf_pkg_srcdir and acjf_pkg_builddir for
   usage in action if found

 * joachim.falk@gmx.de--2004-jf-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.1--patch-25
   
 * Merge from joachim.falk@gmx.de--2006-common-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.2 branch
 - Added support for pkginclude subdir which contains the public headers of the project

 * joachim.falk@gmx.de--2004-jf-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.1--patch-26
   
 * Merge from joachim.falk@gmx.de--2006-common-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.2 branch
 - Use acjf_pkgfound to signal if ACJF_NEED_PKG found the package
   ACJF_NEED_PKG now unset
    - acjf_pkgdir
    - acjf_pkg_srcdir
    - acjf_pkg_builddir
    - pkg_<pkgname>_srcdir
    - pkg_<pkgname>_builddir
   if the package was not found.

 * joachim.falk@gmx.de--2004-jf-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.1--patch-27
   
 * Merge from joachim.falk@gmx.de--2006-common-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.2 branch
 - Fixed annoying problem of using symbolic makefile variables
   $(top_srcdir) and $(top_builddir) in PKGNAME_INCLUDE, PKGNAME_LDFLAGS,
   AM_CPPFLAGS, and AM_LDFLAGS. Now this shell variables can be used
   without modification in the configure runtime environment.

 * joachim.falk@gmx.de--2004-jf-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.1--patch-28
   
 * Merge from joachim.falk@gmx.de--2006-common-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.2 branch
 - Eliminate forgotten debug echo FOO, echo BAR

 * joachim.falk@gmx.de--2004-jf-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.1--patch-29
   
 * Merge from joachim.falk@gmx.de--2006-common-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.2 branch
 - Use absolute path of header for header compilation, fixes the
   case where the header to compile is not directly in the compiler
   include path

 * joachim.falk@gmx.de--2004-jf-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.1--patch-30
   
 * Merge from joachim.falk@gmx.de--2006-common-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.2 branch
 - Do not overwrite pkgincludedir if pkgincludeprefix is not defined

 * joachim.falk@gmx.de--2004-jf-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.1--patch-31
   
 * Merge from joachim.falk@gmx.de--2006-common-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.2 branch
 - ACJF_CHECK_PKG and ACJF_NEED_PKG now add not only
   pkg_<pkgname>_srcdir/pkginclude but also
   pkg_<pkgname>_builddir/pkginclude to the include path

 * joachim.falk@gmx.de--2004-jf-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.1--patch-32
   
 * Merge from joachim.falk@gmx.de--2006-common-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.2 branch
 - Added regression test script for jfsugar.m4

 * joachim.falk@gmx.de--2004-jf-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.1--patch-33
   
 * Merge from joachim.falk@gmx.de--2006-common-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.2 branch
 - Added one more regression test for ACJF_M4_PATH_BASENAME

 * joachim.falk@gmx.de--2004-jf-stuff/BuildSystem--mainline--0.1--patch-34
   
 * Fixed doxygen.m4 to work with automake1.10

